<body>
    <h1>TheKawaCompany Complete API Documentation</h1>
    <p><strong>Project:</strong> TheKawaCompany E-commerce Backend</p>
    <p><strong>Generated From:</strong> Current Laravel routes and API controllers in this project</p>
    <p><strong>Base URL (Apache/XAMPP):</strong> <code>http://localhost/theKawaCompany/public</code></p>
    <p><strong>API Prefix:</strong> <code>/api</code></p>
    <p class="small">Note: Agar aap XAMPP Apache use kar rahe hain to API base URL <code>http://localhost/theKawaCompany/public/api</code> hoga.</p>

    <h2>Authentication</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Auth System: Laravel Sanctum</li>
        <li>Customer/Admin secured endpoints: <code>Authorization: Bearer {token}</code></li>
        <li>Admin-only endpoints: <code>auth:sanctum</code> + <code>role:admin</code></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Standard Response Shape</h2>
    <pre>{
  "status": true,
  "message": "Success message",
  "data": {}
}</pre>
    <pre>{
  "status": false,
  "errors": {
    "field": ["Validation message"]
  }
}</pre>

    <h2>1. Auth APIs</h2>
    <table>
        <tr><th>Method</th><th>Endpoint</th><th>Auth</th><th>Description</th></tr>
        <tr><td>POST</td><td>/api/auth/register</td><td>Public</td><td>Register new customer account</td></tr>
        <tr><td>POST</td><td>/api/auth/login</td><td>Public</td><td>Login and receive Sanctum token</td></tr>
        <tr><td>POST</td><td>/api/auth/logout</td><td>Customer/Admin</td><td>Logout current token</td></tr>
        <tr><td>POST</td><td>/api/auth/refresh</td><td>Customer/Admin</td><td>Refresh auth token</td></tr>
        <tr><td>GET</td><td>/api/auth/profile</td><td>Customer/Admin</td><td>Get logged-in profile with roles</td></tr>
        <tr><td>PUT</td><td>/api/auth/profile</td><td>Customer/Admin</td><td>Update name/email/phone</td></tr>
        <tr><td>POST</td><td>/api/auth/change-password</td><td>Customer/Admin</td><td>Change current password</td></tr>
    </table>
    <pre>{
  "name": "Test Customer",
  "email": "customer@example.com",
  "phone": "9999999999",
  "password": "password",
  "password_confirmation": "password"
}</pre>

    <h2>2. Address APIs</h2>
    <table>
        <tr><th>Method</th><th>Endpoint</th><th>Auth</th><th>Description</th></tr>
        <tr><td>POST</td><td>/api/addresses</td><td>Customer/Admin</td><td>Create address</td></tr>
        <tr><td>GET</td><td>/api/addresses</td><td>Customer/Admin</td><td>List own addresses</td></tr>
        <tr><td>GET</td><td>/api/addresses/{id}</td><td>Customer/Admin</td><td>Get single address</td></tr>
        <tr><td>PUT</td><td>/api/addresses/{id}</td><td>Customer/Admin</td><td>Update address</td></tr>
        <tr><td>DELETE</td><td>/api/addresses/{id}</td><td>Customer/Admin</td><td>Delete address</td></tr>
        <tr><td>POST</td><td>/api/addresses/{id}/set-default</td><td>Customer/Admin</td><td>Mark address as default</td></tr>
    </table>

    <h2>3. Category APIs</h2>
    <table>
        <tr><th>Method</th><th>Endpoint</th><th>Auth</th><th>Description</th></tr>
        <tr><td>GET</td><td>/api/categories</td><td>Public</td><td>List root categories; admin can request inactive too</td></tr>
        <tr><td>GET</td><td>/api/categories/{category}</td><td>Public</td><td>Get single category by id</td></tr>
        <tr><td>GET</td><td>/api/categories/{category}/subcategories</td><td>Public</td><td>List subcategories</td></tr>
        <tr><td>POST</td><td>/api/categories</td><td>Admin</td><td>Create category/subcategory</td></tr>
        <tr><td>PUT</td><td>/api/categories/{category}</td><td>Admin</td><td>Update category/subcategory</td></tr>
        <tr><td>DELETE</td><td>/api/categories/{category}</td><td>Admin</td><td>Delete category/subcategory</td></tr>
    </table>

    <h2>4. Product APIs</h2>
    <table>
        <tr><th>Method</th><th>Endpoint</th><th>Auth</th><th>Description</th></tr>
        <tr><td>GET</td><td>/api/products</td><td>Public</td><td>List products with category, images, variants</td></tr>
        <tr><td>GET</td><td>/api/products/{slug}</td><td>Public</td><td>Get product detail by slug</td></tr>
        <tr><td>POST</td><td>/api/products</td><td>Admin</td><td>Create product with optional nested variants array</td></tr>
        <tr><td>PUT</td><td>/api/products/{id}</td><td>Admin</td><td>Update product and sync nested variants</td></tr>
        <tr><td>DELETE</td><td>/api/products/{id}</td><td>Admin</td><td>Delete product</td></tr>
        <tr><td>GET</td><td>/api/admin/products/{id}</td><td>Admin</td><td>Admin product detail by id</td></tr>
    </table>
    <pre>{
  "category_id": 1,
  "subcategory_id": 2,
  "name": "Chamomile Bliss Tea",
  "short_description": "Relaxing herbal tea",
  "description": "Full description",
  "ingredients": "Chamomile, Lemongrass",
  "tea_type": "Herbal",
  "status": true,
  "variants": [
    {
      "variant_name": "Premium Pack",
      "size": "250g",
      "color": "Green",
      "sku": "CHAM-250-GRN",
      "price": 499,
      "stock": 25,
      "status": true
    }
  ]
}</pre>

